    "2617987": {
      "title": "Bio++: a set of C++ libraries for sequence analysis, phylogenetics, molecular evolution and population genetics",
      "abstract": "Background ::: A large number of bioinformatics applications in the fields of bio-sequence analysis, molecular evolution and population genetics typically share input/ouput methods, data storage requirements and data analysis algorithms. Such common features may be conveniently bundled into re-usable libraries, which enable the rapid development of new methods and robust applications."
